OL,3,C'Worst thing I've ever seen' - family
OL,4,Creact to footage of man killed by
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FThe brother of a man killed by a
OL,8,Fmachete on the street in Castle
OL,9,FBromwich has told ITV News that
OL,10,Fwatching the footage of his death was
OL,11,F'the worst thing he has ever had to
OL,12,Fwatch.'
OL,14,FYesterday two people were given life
OL,15,Fsentences for the murder of Kelvin
OL,16,FWard on April 18th 2023. They will be
OL,17,Fin prison for a minimum of 29 years
OL,18,Fand 19 years respectively.
