OL,3,C'Worst thing I've ever seen' - family
OL,4,Creact to footage of man killed by
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FThe pair were part of a gang of four
OL,8,Fwho rammed their car into one Kelvin's
OL,9,Fson was driving, in an attack aimed at
OL,10,Fthe 19 year old. Kelvin's son escaped
OL,11,Fhis attackers but three of them turned
OL,12,Fhis attention to them and killed him
OL,13,Fwith a machete.
OL,15,FThe attack was captured on CCTV and
OL,16,Fshown in court.
