OL,3,C'Worst thing I've ever seen' - family
OL,4,Creact to footage of man killed by
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FKelvin's brother David Ward told ITV
OL,8,FNews Central," It's the hardest thing
OL,9,FI've ever had to watch. To see it and
OL,10,Fto see the guy plunge the knife into
OL,11,Fmy brother, it's just awful.
OL,13,FIt's the shock, that kind of horror,
OL,14,Fthat kind of disassociation that this
OL,15,Fisn't really happening but it's your
OL,16,Fbrother and you're looking there and
OL,17,Fthere's this guy stab him like he's a
OL,18,Fpiece of meat and then run off like a
OL,19,Fcoward. It is absolute desolation."
