OL,7,FDavid joined family members in court
OL,8,Fyesterday to see . He said that he is
OL,9,Fpleased with the outcome, although
OL,10,Fwishes life meant '80-90 years.'
OL,12,FReacting to seeing the four in the
OL,13,Fdock he told us, "you see these people
OL,14,Fand they've taken my brother away, so
OL,15,Fall the stories, all the laughter we
OL,16,Fwould have had were taken away.
