OL,3,C'Worst thing I've ever seen' - family
OL,4,Creact to footage of man killed by
OL,5,Cmachete
OL,7,FSo to see them in the dock before the
OL,8,Ftrial, they were fist bumping each
OL,9,Fother and laughing and joking between
OL,10,Fthemselves and for me I see people who
OL,11,Fdidn't have any remorse, and I think
OL,12,Fthat is the dark side of people."
OL,14,FDavid hopes that the convictions for
OL,15,FKelvin's murder deters others from
OL,16,Ftaking a knife out of the house and
OL,17,Fsays that his family will have to live
OL,18,Fwith the effects of knife crime
OL,19,Feveryday.
